docs/guides/01-getting-started.md
     1тЖТ# Getting Started тАж
     3тЖТ## Installing Superstruct
     5тЖТTo install Superstruct run:
     6тЖТ
     7тЖТ```bash
     8тЖТnpm install --save superstruct
     9тЖТ```
    10тЖТ
    11тЖТAnd then you can import it:
    12тЖТ
    13тЖТ```ts
    14тЖТimport { object, string, number } from 'superstruct'
    15тЖТ
    16тЖТconst User = object({
    17тЖТ  id: number(),
    18тЖТ  name: string(),
    19тЖТ})
    20тЖТ```
    21тЖТ
    22тЖТIf you'd like, you can use a wildcard import:
    23тЖТ
    24тЖТ```ts
    25тЖТimport * as s from 'superstruct'
    26тЖТ
    27тЖТconst User = s.object({
    28тЖТ  id: s.number(),
    29тЖТ  name: s.string(),
    30тЖТ})
    31тЖТ```
    32тЖТ
      тЖТтАж
