docs/resources/links.md
     1тЖТ# Resources
     3тЖТA few resources that are helpful for building with Superstruct.
     4тЖТ
     5тЖТ## Libraries
     7тЖТ- [`bumpover`](https://github.com/doodlewind/bumpover) helps you transform data asynchronously with simple rules, whose validation API is built with Superstruct.
     8тЖТ- [micro-superstruct](https://github.com/brandon93s/micro-superstruct) allows you to easily validate your [Micro](https://github.com/zeit/micro) API request body and query string parameters using Superstruct.
